title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Spicing life up with family activities offers excitement and joy for all involved. Perhaps you collaborate to plan a gathering that brings relatives or close friends together in an unusual way, like a reunion aboard a cruise or a destination wedding. Or with less fanfare, you decide to dine out someplace exotic. Transform the tense opposition between loving Venus and shocking Uranus into an opportunity for paving new grooves with familiar people. Dont be discouraged by initial rejections. Your enthusiasm, perseverance, and sheer originality are enticing, even if others dont want to admit it. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
